Random Reads: Lookup Doc by ID
benchmark_code:
def get(self) -> int:
        cnt = 0
        cnt_found = 0
        t0 = time()
        for doc_id in self.tasks.doc_ids_to_query:
            match = self.tdb.get(doc_id)
            cnt += 1
            cnt_found += 0 if (match is None) else 1
            dt = time() - t0
            if dt > self.max_seconds_per_query:
                break
        print(f'---- {cnt} ops: {cnt_found} ID matches')
        return cnt
